Convert enrichList to data.frame

Source: R/jamenrich-base.r
enrichList2df.Rd

Convert enrichList to data.frame

enrichList2df(
  enrichList,
  keyColname = c("itemsetID", "ID", "Name"),
  geneColname = c("geneNames", "Genes"),
  geneCountColname = c("geneCount", "geneHits", "Count"),
  pvalueColname = c("P-value", "pvalue", "Pval"),
  pvalueFloor = 1e-200,
  msigdbGmtT = NULL,
  geneDelim = "[,/ ]",
  verbose = FALSE,
  debug = 0,
  ...
)
